      <h1 class='title'>World Peace</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c269WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_269ws' title='Col. 269WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c269WS' name='column_269ws' href='#column_269ws' rel='bookmark'>269WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06336'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_314'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-jeremy-corbyn' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_314' title='Link to this speech by Mr Jeremy Corbyn' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-jeremy-corbyn" title="Mr Jeremy Corbyn">Jeremy Corbyn</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06336">To ask the Prime Minister what recent discussions he has had with President Bush concerning world peace. [89202]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06337'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_315'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tony-blair' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_315' title='Link to this speech by Mr Tony Blair' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-tony-blair" title="Mr Tony Blair">The Prime Minister</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06337">I am in regular telephone contact with President Bush about threats to world peace, and had three meetings with him last year, most recently at the NATO summit in Prague in November. At a joint press conference there, we said that we shared the strong conviction that we must work together to make the world a more peaceful place.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
